  <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-bark-500">
    This is the first calculator in the <a href="/clusters/indoor-plants/" class="text-moss-700 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-moss-900">Indoor Plants cluster</a> — more houseplant-focused tools are on the way.
  </p>

